{"tid":1336713,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】騰訊旗下兩遊戲獲批版號","createTime":"2019-07-21T05:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T09:51:25.000Z","uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5d1082754d3f12a95955819ef26b48f832b53b94","tid":1336713,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"原國家新聞出版廣電總局官方公布，今年第四批進口遊戲版號已經下發，總數為24個。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當中，騰訊控股(00700)旗下的競類遊戲《火箭聯盟》及射擊遊戲《王牌戰士》亦在名單之上；網易旗下兩遊戲《實況：王者集結》及《軒轅劍龍舞雲山》亦獲批。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千升了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f643427518fc623f05e1de955ba454a310db86c","tid":1336713,"uid":162511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:11:54.000Z","msg":"又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065ca3efd54d7f10e7ede65c02f546c64a598b78","tid":1336713,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:16:03.000Z","msg":"仆街又夾"},{"pid":"b103308ac16e435f1d5e8e7519850d0a33f52411","tid":1336713,"uid":85168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"buy the rumour sell the fact 千跌了"},{"pid":"bb8b77aff266dc1e3fbeb50472203fd7c1879673","tid":1336713,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:20:37.000Z","msg":"和平使者<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"b7f747e16308f0f06c11f09b9cb9fd1a8bcf00c9","tid":1336713,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f643427518fc623f05e1de955ba454a310db86c","tid":1336713,"uid":162511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T06:11:54.000Z","msg":"又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}